{"tid":1516150,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］藍屍廢老菊花不保","createTime":"2019-08-29T12:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T16:10:27.000Z","uid":269515,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"47479a6e0c820429076be3ea2ae9e49804cc1d50","tid":1516150,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:46:35.000Z","msg":"岩岩起西鐵廁所見到門板有人用marker寫標語 <br />\n邊個絲打做架 <br />\n小妹予以強烈譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PfFvApT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPfFvApT.jpg&h=45dda211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一諗到d廢老肚痛 坐起到對住堆字10幾分鐘 <br />\n嬲又撕唔到 行過隔離果格又見到 我都登佢地個菊花痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果十分鐘內同藍屍廢老就可以同巴絲們慢慢對話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBEtween 大家千祈千祈唔好用marker寫 <br />\n你地知啦 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">油性筆難洗</span></span> 唔好辛苦清潔姐姐啦 <br />\n抗爭係唔可以影響到人同埋要匿起屋企架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要畫就匿起屋企廁所畫啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵雖然出賣港人 大家唔好搞佢啦</span> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">禍不及廁所呀</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n小妹呼籲大家千祈千祈唔好做mk仔 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拎d鎖鑰刻字 </span></span><br />\n你知啦 marker難洗都洗到 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">刻落去嘅話道門要拆過都似</span></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>要用黨鐵d錢 都係果句啦 <br />\n黨鐵雖然出賣港人 大家唔好搞佢啦</strong></span> </span><br />\n<br />\n如果佢地去公廁<br />\n公廁入面寫港英餘孽林鄭月娥果類野<br />\n你知啦 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">爆石係思考人生嘅好機會 </span><br />\n如果佢地見到d長輩圖類嘅文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者指名道姓叫佢地唔好投奶共走狗做議員<br />\n唔好食邊間餐廳<br />\n<br />\n大家都知啦<br />\n公園最多長者<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">公廁又冇cctv</span><br />\n好驚巴絲們俾人秋後/追打呀<br />\n大家唔好亂寫啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5932b26d8b125f1af1ceebdbc2bbb7e303dd94a0","tid":1516150,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:49:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />夜晚十點嗌埋活動日期呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">八三一．遮打見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n九月一，機場見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n九月二．罷工！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6nOAxk7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6nOAxk7.png&h=6eb30bf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jG8ssjZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjG8ssjZ.png&h=d307d020&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/toKLUzN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtoKLUzN.png&h=6967c3bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eab31ee49ee5a8229705609878d22b95958affce","tid":1516150,"uid":269515,"like":